    "causal_summary": "Packet 008 Phase 2 sweep surfaced 3 local-LLM retrieval defects in cat-24--local-llm-query-intelligence: 402 synonymy-across-vocabularies, 408 compound-concept-synthesis, 409 LLM-made-memory-recall. Codex K (commit `8ec4f1491`) implemented memory-side fixes (SQL + trigger-lane + reranking) that closed 402+408 substantially. Scenario **409 remains PARTIAL** because the playbook predicate requires 8/10 top-3 recall under `memory_quick_search` and the active embedding model — `unsloth-embeddinggemma-300m-GGUF` 768-dim q8 — has measurable paraphrase weakness: cosine 0.2829 between \"constitutional importance tier 5\" and \"always-surface memory entries\" (semantically equivalent in our domain).",
